    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, \"vastly superior\" seems a bit strong for a science project. isn't there stuff like mining for wind turbines or what happens to the blades after they break? and i thought gas was better for some things like reliability? isn't it more complicated than just \"clean\" vs \"dirty\"?",
