    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you on the pollution part, but saying everything else is \"manageable\" feels like you're taking a side. what about the ecological impact of mining all that lithium and rare earths for the batteries needed to make wind reliable? seems like we're just swapping one environmental problem for another. wouldn't an objective view look at both sides as having serious downsides?",
